whether it's rumor or gossip,

56
00:02:40,919 --> 00:02:42,520
tell me everything you know.

57
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,120
Though His Majesty hasn't yet married,

58
00:02:45,520 --> 00:02:47,120
he has countless concubines.

59
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:49,159
