79
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,520
If He An wants to remain emperor,

80
00:03:26,080 --> 00:03:27,639
he must have no heirs.

81
00:03:28,879 --> 00:03:30,479
So that's what the Regent meant.

82
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:32,599
Why was this agreement made through me?

83
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:33,879
Is

84
00:03:34,960 --> 00:03:35,879
the empress dowager

85
00:03:37,120 --> 00:03:38,280
an accomplice?

86
00:03:41,080 --> 00:03:41,919
But

87
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:46,000
