88
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:47,159
Your Majesty,

89
00:03:47,639 --> 00:03:49,360
His Majesty has reigned for three years.

90
00:03:49,719 --> 00:03:50,840
He's now of age,

91
00:03:51,120 --> 00:03:52,000
yet remains unmarried.

92
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,719
Why do you think that is?

93
00:03:55,719 --> 00:03:56,680
It seems

94
00:03:57,159 --> 00:03:59,960
