would commence.

97
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,080
Thus,

98
00:04:07,240 --> 00:04:07,879
he couldn't

99
00:04:07,879 --> 00:04:09,680
legitimately control the court anymore.

100
00:04:09,800 --> 00:04:10,479
Right?

101
